snippet.title: Penacony Travel  Promotion Cartoon: Tick-Tock! Come Dream With Us! | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
Who could have thought  that a place like this could exist amidst the vast, scintillating heavens:
The people here have  closed their eyes, but none are asleep even with the striking of midnight.
In the splendor of this  city, things of material value are little more than dirt.
Beloved guests, welcome  to Penacony! Follow your amusing guide, Clockie, and embark with us upon this  incomparable planet woven from the fabric of dreams!

English Voice:
Clockie — Niko Gerentes
Hamster Ball Knight —  Jacob Craner
